"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-01-fans-go-crazy-simone-biles-shows-off-brilliant-new-necklace-winning-olympic-gold-21345423\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles continued her Olympic redemption story by claiming her second gymnastics gold in Paris and sixth overall.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.561198051771846e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles helped Team USA pick up gold in a team event earlier this week and continue her impressive form in the individual all-around final on Thursday evening.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9877268535719366, \"rank\": 0.012188475796960684, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American won this title back at Rio in 2016 and was favourite in Tokyo five years later but pulled out after suffering from the 'twisties'.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 283, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999517475453443, \"rank\": 4.677499801464232e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999991905923344, \"rank\": 8.094083520736845e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9980581958933699, \"rank\": 0.0019455318732865537, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles produced a sensational display in the Paris event, becoming the oldest winner of her sport's blue-riband event for 72 years.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.561198051771846e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After beating Brazil's Rebeca Andrade and defending champion Sunisa Lee to gold, Biles showed off a new necklace - a sparkly goat in reference to her tag as the greatest of all time.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9748460695397401, \"rank\": 0.018212209950823934, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}, {\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'A lot of people love calling me the GOAT, they always do it, so I thought it would be really special if I got one made,' Biles toldEurosportwhen asked about her new piece of jewellery.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The haters hate it so I love it even more.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a special part of me that I have him, as well as a stuffed goat back at the village, just as a reminder to me that I can do this and I have done it before.'\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles finished with an overall score of 59.131, with Brazil's Rebeca Andrade taking silver and defending champion Sunisa Lee.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9748460695397401, \"rank\": 0.018212209950823934, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}, {\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Oh my gosh I am ecstatic with my performances,' Biles told Eurosport.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was all pretty good in my opinion, I could not have asked for more.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was a little worried about Rebeca, we were neck and neck basically the whole way through and she's a phenomenal gymnast.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am glad she was there to push me.'\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reacting to Biles' latest gold-winning performance, BBC commentator Matt Baker said: 'What a comeback, wow.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9779057185277079, \"rank\": 0.022404525883042016, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"score\": 0.9803545262364683, \"rank\": 0.016653655997920964, \"text\": \"Matt Baker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That was absolutely incredible - on so many levels.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles is back where she belongs.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1734, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Absolutely another level.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You can feel the admiration and respect from everyone here - that is the way to do it.\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goodness me it wasn't easy, it had its ups-and-downs, but surely that is your champion.'\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The GOAT necklace??\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Omg!\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes Simone Biles!\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"!#OlympicGames  simone biles wearing a goat necklace is iconic \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082  SIMONE BILES WEARING A DIMAOND GOAT NECKLACE!\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"YESSSSSSSS.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0090\\u0090\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0090\\u0090  Simone Biles wearing a goat necklace\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0092\\u00af  SIMONE BILES IS THAT A GOAT NECKLACE  Is that a goat necklace??\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u00a3\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u00a3 I will repeat, SIMONE BILES IS THAT GIRL \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u008f\\u00f0\\u009f\\u008f\\u00be  Simone Biles immediately putting on a necklace of a diamond goat is honestly the energy I am absolutely here for.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Love her.\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nah sorry Simone Biles putting on her goat necklace after coming 1st and the coach shouting period!\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodium_hydride\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nah\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodium_hydride\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodium_hydride\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We love to see it  Terrifyingly, for her rivals at least, Biles could yet add three more golds to her collection ahead of three individual finals.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is due to take part in the vault final on Saturday and the beam and floor finals on Monday.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles holds the record for most women's all-around world titles and most world championship medals.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before Paris 2024 she was already the most decorated gymnast with 37 world medals.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2902, \"end\": 2912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.21684789726181e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic tennis ball girl goes viral for giving Novak Djokovic a flirty look  ArrowMORE:Andy Murray heartbroken to miss out on 'fairytale ending' at Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:Hollywood megastar set to perform death-defying stunt during Olympics closing ceremony  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3158, \"end\": 3172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0